# Copy to .env.local and fill in ONE of the two options below.
# Both keys are read ONLY on the server (app/api/* route handlers via lib/llm.ts)
# and never reach the client bundle.
# Without any key the app still works — it serves an offline draft tree.
#
# IMPORTANT: never commit real keys. .env.local is gitignored — keep secrets there.

# --- Option A: Anthropic API (direct) ---
# Get a key at console.anthropic.com
# Default model: claude-haiku-4-5-20251001 (cheap). Override:
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Option B: OpenRouter (100+ models, one key) ---
# Get a key at openrouter.ai
# Default model: google/gemini-flash-1.5 (very cheap). Override:
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=openai/gpt-4o-mini
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=anthropic/claude-haiku
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...
